Package: greenSD
Type: Package
Title: Access and Analyze Greenspace Seasonality Data Cubes Using Spatial Queries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Xiaohao",
      family = "Yang",
      email = "xiaohaoy111@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    ))
Description: Provides functions to access and extract multi-band greenspace seasonality data
  cubes derived from Sentinel-2 imagery, available for 1028 major global cities.
  Users can download data using bounding boxes, city names, or coordinates, and sample
  values at specific points. Built-in support for data filtering by year and time window.
URL: https://github.com/billbillbilly/greenSD
BugReports: https://github.com/billbillbilly/greenSD/issues
